snippet.title: Longplay of Barbie Horse Adventures: Blue Ribbon Race
snippet.description:
Longplay of Barbie Horse Adventures: Blue Ribbon Race, played as the NTSC version on the Game Boy Advance. This game's version was released on Sep. 17th, 2003. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

00:00 - Start
00:55 - Primrose Hill Village
03:47 - Primrose Hill Farm
11:34 - Buttercup Mountain Trail
15:06 - Pine Valley Race
21:44 - National Park Trail
30:11 - National Park Race
37:26 - Primrose Hill Final Race
41:33 - Minigame: Horseshoes
42:05 - Minigame: Happy Trails
43:45 - Minigame: Shoe Shuffle
44:23 - Minigame: Maze Valley
46:01 - Credits

By: DeShelly
